headline: Realty Income GIC Logistics Push And What It Means For Valuation
summary: Realty Income (NYSE:O) has entered into a partnership with Singapore’s sovereign wealth fund GIC focused on U.S. logistics properties. The collaboration includes a large joint venture aimed at acquiring and managing logistics assets across the United States. This agreement marks a move by Realty Income to diversify its funding sources and expand beyond its traditional net lease retail footprint.
